line_1: Sure never creature was so charming!
line_2: How sleek's the skin! how speck'd like ermine!

line_1: there are times when all that I do is most charming;
line_2: at others, the very best jest is alarming.

line_1: Was the first that presented her Person so charming,
line_2: Lady TETTATON's Sister, Miss FUBBY FATARMIN,
